Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了？嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  由由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上越發地冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.38,0:00:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真不想從被窩裡出來
